    "timestamp": "2026-04-22T17:17:36.808Z",
    "innerText": "What We Offer\nYour end-to-end billing service.\nInsurance Verification\n\nCreate a customized complete breakdown with common codes for your office and questions. Verified plans inputted into your software with complete breakdown attached.\n\n\nPayment Posting\n\nPost payments within 24 hours. Keep a clean ledger at all times with accurate and up-to-date information.\n\n\nPatient Billing\n\nThrough customized text, email, or snail mail flows - allow patients to pay their balance conveniently.\n\n\nDetailed Analytics\n\nMeasure each step of the process and identify problems before they become one.\n\n\nClaim Submission & Follow-up\n\nAttachments, clean claims, and denial follow-up off your plate and on to ours.\n",
    "outerHTML": "<div class=\"padding-global padding-section-medium bottom-off\"><div class=\"container-small\"><div class=\"eyebrow_holder\"><div class=\"eyebrow\">What We Offer</div></div><div class=\"heading-holder\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2 text-color-white\">Your end-to-end billing service.</h2></div><div class=\"offer-wrapper tablet-hidden\"><div class=\"offer_grid top\"><div id=\"w-node-_9e8b1761-de33-18d7-9e92-fbb63b507d96-2d042276\" data-w-id=\"9e8b1761-de33-18d7-9e92-fbb63b507d96\" class=\"offer_card\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; will-change: transform;\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683674a9a7c387ee381dc6c9_insurance-verif.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"offer_card-img\"></div><div class=\"offer_card-wrapper center\"><div class=\"offer-card_copy-top\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h4\">Insurance Verification</h3><p class=\"text-size-small text-color-muted\">Create a customized complete breakdown with common codes for your office and questions. Verified plans inputted into your software with complete breakdown attached.<br></p></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683784d43788c93a6c162abd_Group%201597881878.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"155\" alt=\"A white card with a light green checkmark inside a darker green cog-shaped badge, and the word 'Verified' in dark text below it.\" class=\"offer-img-1\"></div></div><div data-w-id=\"b8359c12-646a-ff18-358f-c0528501ae91\" class=\"offer_card\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; will-change: transform;\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683674a9e3793a7609f7b59c_payment-posting-bg.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"offer_card-img\"></div><div class=\"offer_card-wrapper horizontal\"><div class=\"offer-card_copy-top\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h4\">Payment Posting</h3><p class=\"text-size-small text-color-muted\">Post payments within 24 hours. Keep a clean ledger at all times with accurate and up-to-date information.<br></p></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683674a9d6f151e419c8104a_payment-posting.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"250\" height=\"130\" alt=\"Two cards displaying dental services. The top card shows 'Composite Fillings' from 'Delta Dental' for '$2,000'. The bottom card shows 'Oral Check up' from 'Delta Dental' for '$250'. Both have a green Delta Dental logo.\" class=\"offer-img2\"></div></div><div class=\"offer_card\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; will-change: transform;\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg-color\"></div></div><div class=\"offer_card-wrapper center text-center\"><div class=\"offer-card_copy-top max-width\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h4\">Patient Billing</h3><p class=\"text-size-small text-color-muted\">Through customized text, email, or snail mail flows - allow patients to pay their balance conveniently.<br></p></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683674a9b9da46e02d464369_patient-billing.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"350\" height=\"65\" alt=\"A light green rounded rectangle card with '$250 Dental Exam and Cleaning' on the left and a green dot next to the word 'PAID' on the right.\" class=\"offer-img3\"></div></div></div><div class=\"offer_grid bottom\"><div id=\"w-node-_01926a6d-5ad7-69e2-e2ab-4749608dd30f-2d042276\" class=\"offer_card\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; will-change: transform;\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg-color\"></div></div><div class=\"offer_card-wrapper space-between\"><div class=\"offer-card_copy-top space-between\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h4\">Detailed Analytics</h3><p class=\"text-size-small text-color-muted\">Measure each step of the process and identify problems before they become one.<br></p></div></div></div><div class=\"offer_card\" style=\"transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0deg) rotateY(0deg) rotateZ(0deg) skew(0deg, 0deg); transform-style: preserve-3d; will-change: transform;\"><div class=\"offer_card-bg\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683789c4614de1f20566ec87_Rectangle%2040038.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1171px) 100vw, 1171px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683789c4614de1f20566ec87_Rectangle%2040038-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683789c4614de1f20566ec87_Rectangle%2040038.avif 1171w\" alt=\"\" class=\"offer_card-img\"></div><div class=\"offer_card-wrapper horizontal\"><div class=\"offer-card_copy-top space-between\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h4 is-smaller\">Claim Submission &amp; Follow-up</h3><p class=\"text-size-small text-color-muted\">Attachments, clean claims, and denial follow-up off your plate and on to ours.<br></p></div><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68362d58021f1b602d042278/683674a9de226591f2a24ecf_claim-submission.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"300\" height=\"270\" alt=\"A white card showing progress or completion of tasks. The first section has 'Delta Dental' with a checkmark and a green 'Finished' button. Below it are placeholder lines of text. The next section has 'CI-14884' with a checkmark, followed by more placeholder lines of text.\" class=\"offer-img4\"></div></div></div></div></div></div>",
